    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The double VANOS unit has been meticulously serviced to ensure peak volumetric efficiency, while the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain structural integrity under high torque loads. Performance is further enhanced by a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a recently refreshed cooling system featuring an upgraded aluminum radiator. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative handling this chassis is known for. While the finish shows light signs of use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain excellence and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
