    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This well-cared-for vehicle offers a fantastic blend of reliability and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with responsible ownership and typical highway use. Inside, the cabin remains highly refined; the smoke-free upholstery is clean and free of tears, and the dashboard is free of cracks or sun damage. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, is in full working order. Under the hood, the engine runs strong and the transmission shifts smoothly, backed by a consistent service history and recent oil change. We have kept detailed records of all preventative maintenance to ensure the car remains dependable. It is a solid, high-quality vehicle that is ready for the road today.",
      "price": 34500.0,
