      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Subjected to a rigorous multi-point inspection, the automobile exhibits the mechanical consistency and aesthetic integrity expected of a high-caliber pre-owned selection. Offering a refined driving experience and a documented history of care, this model stands as a testament to enduring quality and sophisticated engineering.",
