      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi everyone! I'm selling my awesome car and it's honestly been a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really great, dependable condition and is ready to hit the road with a new owner today! I've made sure to keep up with everything so you can just hop in and go. It\u2019s perfect for anyone needing a solid, stylish vehicle that won't let them down. I'm super easy to work with, so just shoot me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 31500.0,
